The paper focuses on the use of deep learning for power allocation in a wireless communication system, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of neural networks for optimization also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the optimization of a complex system, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
